INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
1. Copy the xfw_init directory to where you expect your http requests
2. Copy the xfw_sites directory to wherever you want to, if you want to keep the individual site files apart from the engine
3. Set the system directories in the index.php file located in the xfw_init directory accordingly
4. Fill the database credentials in the config_sample.php file located also in the xfw_init directory and rename it to config.php
5. Import the database from xfw.sql
